  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p565625/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201401/2f255665a92f4c62bd678ca214ddd316.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\tChen Guangbiao is an <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/audacious\" target=\"_blank\">audacious</a> man, and not just because he wants to buy the New York Times for $1 billion (or $2 billion or $3 billion).陈光标是个大胆的人，不仅仅因为他想以10亿美元 （也有可能是20亿或30亿美元)买《纽约时报》。</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em;\">One of China's top 400 richest people, he was estimated to have a personal fortune of worth $740 million in 2012, but how he's really made his name is by high-</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/profile\" target=\"_blank\">profile</a><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;charity&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/donation\" target=\"_blank\">donations</a><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;&mdash; something he brands &quot;flashy&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/philanthropy\" target=\"_blank\">philanthropy</a><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em;\">.&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em;\">作为中国前400名富豪之一，他的身价在2012年时就被估计值7.4亿美元，但是真正让他家喻户晓的是他高调的给慈善机构捐款&mdash;&mdash;他称作&ldquo;浮夸的慈善事业。&rdquo;</span></p>\n<p>\n\tOne interesting insight into Chen's mindset might be to look at his English-language business card, one of a number of promotional materials he gives out to U.S. journalists. We're not sure quite how Chen got all those titles on the right, but it's incredible anyway:观察陈光标心态的一个有趣方法是看他的英文名片，这是他给美国记者的众多材料之一。我们不确定他是如何获得这些头衔的，但无论如何，这令人难以置信：</p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201401/154a104cec1e4012b7d302ceb8fb1246.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em;\"><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><strong>沪江小编：</strong></span>陈光标英文名片上的头衔包括&ldquo;中国最具影响力的人&rdquo;、&ldquo;中国最杰出的慈善家&rdquo;、&ldquo;中国精神领袖&rdquo;、&ldquo;</span>中国地震救援英雄<span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em;\">&rdquo;等。</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em;\">如此有土豪气质的名片让人不禁联想到前些天去世的邵逸夫先生，同样是慈善，到底是大肆宣传扩大知名度还是默默付出就好？</span></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p565625/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p565625\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p564702/\">外媒看中国：“老公寄存处”商场兴起</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p565177/\">狗不理咖啡？狗不理收购美咖啡巨头</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p565082/\">美国多地极寒天气：组图告诉你美国有多冷</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p565153/\">《神探夏洛克》编剧：还有第四季和第五季</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p558651/\">韩国画家恶搞名画：当经典遭遇苹果</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p564713/\">只因天太冷！美国囚犯越狱又回头</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p564668/\">总是一个人？孤单时你可以做的9件事</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p564309/\">BBC看中国腐女：就爱看基情《神探夏洛克》</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p565508/\">中日驻英大使交锋BBC 中方引丘吉尔名言驳斥</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a h